%% Diagram: S3 multipart parallel parts flow with bounded concurrency
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (worker pool)
    participant A as App API
    participant S as S3 / R2 / GCS

    C->>A: POST /uploads { key, size }
    A->>S: CreateMultipartUpload
    S-->>A: UploadId
    A-->>C: UploadId + presigned PUT URLs (per part)

    Note over C: Schedule parts on a bounded pool\n(typ. 3-6 in flight)
    par Worker 1
        C->>S: PUT part 1 (5+ MiB)
        S-->>C: 200 OK + ETag1
    and Worker 2
        C->>S: PUT part 2
        S-->>C: 200 OK + ETag2
    and Worker N
        C->>S: PUT part N
        S-->>C: 200 OK + ETagN
    end

    Note over C: Failed parts re-queued\nOther workers keep draining
    C->>A: POST /complete { UploadId, [(n, ETag)] }
    A->>S: CompleteMultipartUpload
    S-->>A: 200 + final ETag
    A-->>C: 201 + canonical object URL
